chordDiagrams

Classes in chordDiagrams used by chordDiagrams
ConfigutaionHolder
          This class is to provide an easy way to access lists of diagrams.
diagram
          This class implements a chord diagram: stores it and has methods to compare it to other diagrams.
DiagramDrawer
          This class provides graphical representations of diagrams (draws diagrams to a bitmap), and provides means to draw collections of diagrams and saving them to files.
FourTGenerator
          Generates all 4T relations for a list of diagrams
FrameGen2
          Generates all distinct chord diagrams for the framed case, modulo link rotation and recoloring.
Orbit
           
OrbitElement
          This class represents an orbit element in an orbit of a diagram under some action.
Relation
          This class stores a diagram relation
UnframedDiagramGenerator
          Generates all distinct chord diagrams for unframed singular knots.
